column6: Description Text
JP
Hungrybox is selecting a character from the roster
Cursor is hovering over Toon Link
Picks Jigglypuff with sun hat costume
Hungrybox practices nair followups during the loading screen stage
Hbox Jigglypuff vs [?] the Villager; 3 stocks|| 7 minutes
Hbox aerial approach as the match begins on Small Battlefield
Hbox hits side b on Villager and sends offstage with fair
Hbox lands multiple aerials offstage|| Villager near blastzone at 74%|| Puff still at 0%
Villager saves jump and makes it back to stage
Hbox lands bair and Villager loses first stock
Villager plants tree at center stage
Villager traps puff with jab on ledge
Puff now at 57%
Villager plants tree underneath the right platform of the stage
Hbox smiles as he uses numerous side b's while the Villager runs away
Villager parries one of the side b's
Villager escapes with Up-B after getting hit by an aerial|| Puff at 77% Villager at 30%
Villager hits Hbox with up air from ledge|| Puff throwing out aerials while coming back to stage
Villager plants another tree under the right platform
Villager uses down-B axe to kill Puff|| now at two stocks apiece
Webcam quickly takes up full screen while Hbox makes an enthusiastic expression at the camera|| then pans back to the game
Villager locks hbox on platform from grab but fails to get the followup after jab
Hbox whiffs Rest and is now sleeping on center of the right platform
Villager charges and releases up smash|| then following up with an up air taking Puff to 52%
Hbox gets hit by a stray lloid rocket.
